headline: This 12 Dividend Stock Portfolio Will Pay Your Bills – Every Week
summary: Most dividend stocks pay quarterly—but your bills don’t. Rent, groceries, gas, surprise car repairs… life doesn’t come once every three months. That’s why some investors are building what’s called a Weekly Paycheck Portfolio—a curated list of dividend-paying stocks staggered to deliver consistent income every week of the year.
